## Installation on Debian Wheezy
##


## 1) Install PySerial (http://pyserial.sourceforge.net)
~# apt-get install python-serial

## 2) Optional: Allow non-root user "username" using the serial port
~# usermod -a -G dialout username
~# reboot

## 3) Unpack
~# tar xvzf '/path/to/PyFingerprint.tar.gz' -C /


## Tests
##

## Enroll finger:
~$ python /usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/PyFingerprint/example_enroll.py

## Search enrolled finger:
~$ python /usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/PyFingerprint/example_search.py

## Delete finger:
~$ python /usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/PyFingerprint/example_delete.py